&lt;h1 id="how-to-be-an-angel-investor"&gt;How to Be an Angel Investor&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;March 2009&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;(This essay is derived from a talk at AngelConf.)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;When we sold our startup in 1998 I thought one day I&amp;rsquo;d do some angel investing. Seven years later I still hadn&amp;rsquo;t started. I put it off because it seemed mysterious and complicated. It turns out to be easier than I expected, and also more interesting.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>